sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/jupyter-web-app
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant StatefulSet as StatefulSet<br/>Managed Resource
    participant Service as Service<br/>ClusterIP 80→8888
    participant VirtualService as Istio VirtualService<br/>(if USE_ISTIO=true)
    participant NotebookPod as Notebook Pod<br/>Jupyter Server :8888
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    Note over User,NotebookPod: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event (Notebook Created)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE StatefulSet<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE Service<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    alt USE_ISTIO=true
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE VirtualService<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    end
    K8sAPI->>StatefulSet: Create Resource
    StatefulSet->>NotebookPod: Launch Pod
    NotebookPod-->>Service: Ready on port 8888
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: UPDATE Notebook Status<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Conditions: Ready
    K8sAPI-->>User: Notebook Ready

    Note over NotebookCtrl,NotebookPod: Flow 2: Idle Notebook Culling
    NotebookCtrl->>NotebookPod: GET /api/kernels<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>Bearer Token/AuthorizationPolicy
    NotebookPod-->>NotebookCtrl: JSON Response<br/>Kernel states + last_activity
    alt Idle Time > CULL_IDLE_TIME (1440m)
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebook<br/>Add annotation: kubeflow-resource-stopped<br/>HTTPS/6443 ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event (Annotation Added)
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: PATCH StatefulSet<br/>Set replicas=0<br/>HTTPS/6443 ServiceAccount Token
        StatefulSet->>NotebookPod: Terminate Pod
    end

    Note over Prometheus,NotebookCtrl: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>NotebookCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>None or TokenReview
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: LIST StatefulSets<br/>HTTPS/6443 ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: StatefulSet List
    NotebookCtrl-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics<br/>notebook_running, notebook_create_total, etc.

    Note over User,NotebookPod: Flow 4: Notebook Restart on ConfigMap Update
    User->>K8sAPI: UPDATE ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/6443 Bearer Token
    User->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebook<br/>Add annotation: notebooks.opendatahub.io/notebook-restart=true<br/>HTTPS/6443 Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event (Annotation Added)
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: DELETE Pod<br/>HTTPS/6443 ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>StatefulSet: Pod Deleted Event
    StatefulSet->>NotebookPod: Recreate Pod (new ConfigMap)
    NotebookPod-->>Service: Ready on port 8888
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebook<br/>Remove restart annotation<br/>HTTPS/6443 ServiceAccount Token
